title: Happy 40th Birthday Amy! + The Frontmen Of Country Perform Their 90’s Hits + The 'Elder vs. Millennial' Championship!
itunes:title: Happy 40th Birthday Amy! + The Frontmen Of Country Perform Their 90’s Hits + The 'Elder vs. Millennial' Championship!
description:
Amy turns 40 today and we find out how she’s celebrating! The Frontmen of Country stop by to perform. They are the lead singers of Lonestar, Little Texas and Restless Heart and they play each of their biggest hits. We crown a champion today in Elder vs. Millennial.
